  >> POP_ORW
  >> `FINITE (count (4 ** n))` by RW_TAC std_ss [FINITE_COUNT]
  >> RW_TAC real_ss [EXTREAL_SUM_IMAGE_NORMAL,extreal_11,extreal_mul_def,extreal_add_def]
  >- (`k + 1 <= 4 ** n` by RW_TAC real_ss [LESS_EQ]
