      >> METIS_TAC [REAL_LT_RDIV_EQ,REAL_POW_DIV,EVAL ``4/2:real``,real_lte])
  >> FULL_SIMP_TAC real_ss [GSYM real_lt]
  >> (MP_TAC o UNDISCH o Q.SPECL [`k`,`count (4 ** n)`] o CONJUNCT2 o Q.SPEC `(\k'. &k' / 2 pow n *
